{"title":"访朝杂咏","authors":["赵扬"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":9,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"访朝杂咏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平壤—元山道中（浪淘沙）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密雨打车篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山色葱茏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茂林深处一径通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想见当年弹雨下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军运倥偬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路转又奇峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云雾迷蒙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此身疑在画图中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨后江山无限好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小立东风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"元山席上为朴在根夫人、具富力妈妈祝酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舍己为人事犹新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中朝友谊血凝成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即今中国好儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长忆朝鲜两母亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朴渊观瀑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻说朴进士，吹笛惊龙宫。龙女赏高洁，委身愿相从。笛声今已杳，惟余水淙淙。临渊窥龙女，飞瀑涤心胸。更喜红领巾，围唱“东方红”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}